msgctxt "2584"
msgid "Akiyama"
msgstr "Akiyama"

msgctxt "2588"
msgid "Talk_No"
msgstr "Talk_No"

msgctxt "2592"
msgid "Man in the Sketch"
msgstr "Hombre del Boceto"

msgctxt "2596"
msgid "Talk_Gakkari"
msgstr "Talk_Gakkari"

msgctxt "2600"
msgid "Talk_Away"
msgstr "Talk_Away"

msgctxt "2604"
msgid "Talk_Yes"
msgstr "Talk_Yes"

msgctxt "56_Akiyama"
msgid "Now, why'd you have to run off like that? Might as well have\\r\n"
"confessed then and there."
msgstr "¿Por que corres de mi? Eso es como una confesión."

msgctxt "68_Man in the Sketch"
msgid "Wait, I just helped out a little! If you're gonna bring\\r\n"
"me in, then at least get the other guys, too!"
msgstr "¡Espera, yo solo ayudé! Si vas a atraparme, ¡Deberás buscar\\r\n"
"a todos los demás!"

msgctxt "80_Akiyama"
msgid "You're yakuza, right? Aren't you supposed to be looking out\\r\n"
"for your boys and what not?"
msgstr "Eres un yakuza, ¿No? Se supone que debes encubrir al resto."

msgctxt "92_Akiyama"
msgid "Guess it doesn't matter. Who are these \"other guys,\" and\\r\n"
"where are they?"
msgstr "No importa. ¿Quienes son los \"otros\" y dónde los encuentro?"

msgctxt "104_Man in the Sketch"
msgid "Over at the docks. You can get there by cab... A bunch of\\r\n"
"'em get together there just about every night."
msgstr "En los muelles. Puedes llegar en taxi... Se reúnen todos\\r\n"
"a la noche."

msgctxt "116_Akiyama"
msgid "There're some youngbloods from my branch and couple of dudes\\r\n"
"from continental Asia, too. You'd better watch yourself－they mean business."
msgstr "Hay jóvenes inexpertos como yo, pero también hay algunos\\r\n"
"que vienen del continente. Ve con cuidado, ellos son peligrosos."

msgctxt "128_Akiyama"
msgid "Good grief... What did I get myself into? Listen here, pal, there are sketches of you all over town. If I were you, I'd turn myself in."
msgstr "Santo cielo... ¿Donde me he metido? Bueno, escucha amigo,\\r\n"
"hay bocetos tuyos por toda la ciudad. Si fuera tú, me entregaría."

msgctxt "140_Man in the Sketch"
msgid "Yes, sir!"
msgstr "¡Sí, señor!"

msgctxt "164_Akiyama"
msgid "(Now to head over to the docks.)"
msgstr "(Hora de ir a los muelles)"

